Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be going now, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:52.07,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 8\NEncounter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Otosaka, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:01:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I welcome you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry it's been so—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our Yusarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just because he's a bit handsome...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to welcome me back, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing that you \Nneed to apologize about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now, we have all of the student council\Nback together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is why I decided\Nthat I'll stick it out with you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}until you have risen back up to normal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, to celebrate your return...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I give you, Otosaka, this magic spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Forget about the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The magic spell of being all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! The memorable\NYusarin's magic spell series, #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The magic spell of being all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:47.62,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusarin! Yusarin! Yusarin! Yusarin! Yusarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the first day she appeared on Move-Asa,\Nthis infamous magic spell idea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,completely destroyed\Nthe fortune-telling segment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a turn-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yusarin, good morning!\NI reserved your new single Hatsunetsu Days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too! Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Myself as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This cheerfulness that is even annoying...\NI'm so thankful of it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I can spend everyday life\Nlike I had always done.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The music video that comes with the first press\Nof my new single Hatsunetsu Days!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a turn-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll head over to the cafeteria ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you. Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a welcome back gift\Nin your own way?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't much meaning to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to eat this limited dish\Nfor the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's obviously being considerate of me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But for now, I'll indulge \Nin his friendliness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy I can eat this again. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really is tasty after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. No matter how many times you eat this,\Nyou don't get sick of eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time to gather up. Let's \Nhurry up and eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is going to show up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so slow...\Nwhat were your zodiac signs again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You always are too sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now that everyone is here, I guess we'll start\Nby watching Kurobane's music video...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That embarrasses me so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to watch it before anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got one rabid fan here,\Nso it's all right even if it's a horrible video.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it! Once me there you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it! Not the side there you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A side glance indicates prone to illness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it! Once me there you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Many likes and dislikes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it! Not the side there you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Faltering home and then all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The worst feverish Friday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm alone I can become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The days where I thought\Nthat are becoming more distant
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My throat is completely parched
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And my voice doesn't reach
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it! Once me there you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it! Not the side there you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I headed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it! Once me there you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it! Not the side there you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, give her some kind of feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, it's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be complimented by Tomori...\NYusarin is so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm going to dock points\Nbecause you just called yourself Yusarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Within your mind, Tomori,\Naround how many points do I have..?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10 points for the singing, 20 points for the song,\N20 points for the costume, 30 points for editing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And -51 points for the \Nsinger being so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,29 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a failing score!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you reevaluate\Nbased on just the music video?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Yusarin is so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's down to 19 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusa is totally looking dumb right now\Nbecause of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like I'm your fan or anything,\Nso as a business, I believe it's a perfect 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty unusual for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Yusarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Yusarin is so happy!\N- For now, I'd like to watch it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The next time is the last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, he's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's not coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why did you gather us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, actually....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Voila!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... these are \Ntickets for a ZHIEND gig.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And, it's for tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZHIEND?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yusa, you didn't know about them?\NIt's the rock band that Tomori loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not rock! It's post-rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Post-rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look it up on Wikipedia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.75,OS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Post-rock is a type of rock music.\NIt has rhythms, chords, melodies, and chord progressions\Nthat aren't in traditional rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I understand it even less...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right here, I have two \Nticket for ZHIEND's gig.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is, what should I do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not comprehending the meaning of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She means, one person gets to go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. But I don't know about\Nthat something-rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their reviews and popularity overseas\Nare super-high, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If your song was a perfect score at 100 points,\NZHIEND would score a million points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think there was a score\Nabove a perfect score!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, do I have any volunteers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much interest, either.\NSo, Otosaka, how about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.\NHow about you go together with Tomori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Hold it.\NWhat's with deciding it by process of elimination?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about Misa?\NI haven't heard Misa's opinion yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go if I can listen to\Na super-fast two-bass at BPM260.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get a super-fast two-bass\Nat BPM260 so please refrain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, that means it's been decided\Nthat Otosaka is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right at a time like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it good every so often?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People do need breathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll plan on going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's blind...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why avoid me? Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that just now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can it be..?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... How... what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to let me eat Modern-yaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're fine with Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talkin' about Modern-yaki. \NMo-der-n-ya-ki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Modern-yaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You too? Nobody knows.\NI'm in Japan, why the hell is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you talking about\Nokonomiyaki with noodles in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That's right, noodles!\NWhere can I eat some?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind it being Hiroshima-yaki,\Nthey have it at any normal okonomiyaki place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have noodles in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By all means, take me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One Hiroshima-yaki, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And a medium draft beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... I'll have some oolong tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, make that two \NHiroshima-yakis , please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I go home, nobody is going\Nto have dinner ready for me anymore...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to get used to this lifestyle soon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that hits the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want to cook it yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, she's blind, so please cook it for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, huh? She's blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there! I'm Sala Shane,\Nthe vocalist for ZHIEND!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I thought!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe Sala dropped by\Nsuch a filthy little okonomiyaki place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll be going to the gig tomorrow!\NA-And, can I get an autograph on a signboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm surprised she can draw that\Nwithout being able to see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And here you go! Please eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The pancake part is really thin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not a Modern-yaki,\Nso there will be differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. But it's still tasty!\NNothing less from Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!\NI'm looking forward to your gig!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I made you pay for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did something bad happen to you recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell from how you breathe\Nand how your voice sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been emitting despair nonstop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you lose someone close to you\Nor something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing... that's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, can you tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just the other day,\NI lost my little sister in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been this kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At least let me\Nput up some smoke for that little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By that, do you mean some incense?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right! That!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, you don't have to go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'd like you to allow me to! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I get it! So \Nplease lift your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... I have one favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I'd like you to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She has a sibling that loves your band.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like that person \Nisn't an ordinary fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're correct. Hold on just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think,\Nthis is the first time I'm calling her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, Tomori here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um... it's me, Otosaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you. This is unusual.\NIs something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I don't want you \Nto be surprised by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm here together with\Nthe vocalist of ZHIEND right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not surprised? You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I believe you. There's no merit for you\Nto tell a lie like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, what do you want?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can meet her, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What would I do by meeting her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me!\NYou can talk to her, and actually I—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I could meet her,\NI wouldn't go out of my way to meet her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love the music and performance of ZHIEND,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I just want to listen to their CDs\Nand watch their gigs. That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And is that all you called for?\NI'm going to hang up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no... that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're beating around the bush... what is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait, they're not close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When do you have to be back by?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:15:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time isn't something to consider.\NIt's fine, you can take me anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, what's important to you\Nis already just as important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But your gig is tomorrow... \Nis it really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The band members and our producer\Nwill make do somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. That helps a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to tell her I don't need dinner...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit, I did it again. \NShe's no longer here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you go with another heavy sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just remind yourself\Nof your little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really do see through everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You just ate moments ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was lunch that we \Nhad. Next up is dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you go on train rides of course it would
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,be a soba place that you eat standing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God! Croquet soba?\NThis menu item is way too amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A miraculous chemistry! I gotta pay my respect\Nto whoever came up with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I ask you one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry this is a delicate question...\Nbut those eyes... are they completely blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can see absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you can write autographs\Nmeans that you weren't born blind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But this is repentance for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Repentance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's like atonement for my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever thought about life?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Life is something you live only once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had dreamed of standing on stage\Nas the front-man for a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But my life was already beyond hope\Nbefore I knew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I couldn't grant myself that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was pitiful at both singing\Nand playing a guitar,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,while on TV, people my age\Nwere showered with praise from their songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I resented God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, that's exactly what you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cheated?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I cheated just for my own greed, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time\Nwhen I was popular in Japan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A social phenomenon,\Na person of the times, that kind of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Immense amount of money moved.\NHow the people around you look at you change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, for the worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you end up troubling your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My little brother got kidnapped once\Nfor ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I ended \Neverything of that sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, I decided I wanted to be\Nthe front-man for a really dull band.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I bartered my eyesight away,\Nand that's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To God, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure\Nyou don't quite understand it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, if such a day ever comes for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to handle it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can see where we're headed to,\Nbut I need you to walk just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry to drag you out\Nto somewhere so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you realize this?\NYou are a really kind person right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't like that in the past, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not self-aware of it,\Nbut you're probably right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've met good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's the case,\NI can't think of anyone other than Tomori.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So she influenced me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're beating around the bush... what is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want your big brother to meet this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:19:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your big brother has been a ZHIEND fan\Nfor a long time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something might happen as a result\Nof him meeting the band's vocalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What would happen?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For instance... he might become sane again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's too good to be true.\NThat'd never happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, I want to bet that it would!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The possibility is not zero.\NSo, please go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm glad...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why do you care so much\Nabout my big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, that's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think, she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more of a person that has knocked down others for my sake...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is something wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a whim...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, how to put it... thank you very much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can you relay to the hospital\Nthat Sala and I are going to visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure. Roger that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what condition he's in right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NPlease have your heart ready for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I can feel how heavy the situation is\Njust from your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The painkillers have worn off again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very strange feeling...\NHey, what is that person doing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's supposedly composing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. This is a lot heavier than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, he looked up to your band,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and he was about to debut\Nfrom a major record label as a guitarist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looking up high
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found a steel tower
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wondering how I would feel
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I fall down
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw deep red
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing for what's far ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always yearning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know why but the beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really want
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May seem to be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Awkward to someone's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki Tomori, can you tell who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember about your little sister Nao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Na...o...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:21:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.94,0:22:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like some sort of \Nmiracle just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Your song was able to wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem happy from the bottom of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me just as happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.63,0:22:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you moved one step forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I was able to spend\Na very fruitful day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,\NI'm planning on going to your gig tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.89,0:22:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Then I'll sing while keeping in mind\Nthat you're out there in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.44,0:22:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the person you care about\Nwill be there too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.53,0:22:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For her sake as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, please do...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So in the end... Tomori,\Nyou were the one that changed me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.88,0:23:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Otosaka here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's me, Tomori.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.68,0:23:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want to hear what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've already heard.\NI'm standing outside the hospital right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we passed each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.02,0:23:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes. I received notice from the nurses,\Nand rushed over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He recognized me, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the first time in a while\Nthat I saw my big brother like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.74,0:23:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes. Your decision was a wonderful one.\NSo, I wanted to give you my thanks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, I'll see you again tomorrow.\NYou haven't forgotten about the gig, have you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.59,0:23:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.10,0:23:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's her gig tomorrow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does it feel so nostalgic?{\i0}
